{{Occupational hazards}}

'''危害消除'''（{{lang|en|Hazard elimination}}）是一種危害管理方式，注重把物件或工序所做成的危害完全消除。危害消除是[[控制等級|控制等級]]五大類方式中最為有效的一種，並應優先使用<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/topics/hierarchy/|title=Hierarchy of Controls|last=|first=|date=2016-07-18|website=U.S. [[美国国家职业安全卫生研究所|美国国家职业安全卫生研究所]]|language=en-us|access-date=2017-03-09|archive-date=2020-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517003808/https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/topics/hierarchy/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYCOSH">{{cite web|url=http://nycosh.org/index.php?page=Hierarchy-of-Hazard-Controls|title=Hierarchy of Hazard Controls|website=New York Committee for Occupational Safety & Health|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305133129/http://nycosh.org/index.php?page=Hierarchy-of-Hazard-Controls|archive-date=2012-03-05|accessdate=2017-03-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="OHS answers">{{cite web|url=http://www.ccohs.ca/oshanswers/hsprograms/hazard_control.html|title=Hazard Control|last=|first=|date=2006-04-20|website={{tsl|en|Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety|}}|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-14|archive-date=2020-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125214725/https://www.ccohs.ca/oshanswers/hsprograms/hazard_control.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不少司法管轄區要求僱主在可行時必須把危害完全消除，不可行之時才可考慮其他選項<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hsaa.ca/effective-representation/hazard-identification-elimination-and-control|title=Hazard Identification, Elimination and Control|website=Health Sciences Association of Alberta|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170314062833/https://www.hsaa.ca/effective-representation/hazard-identification-elimination-and-control|archive-date=2017-03-14|access-date=2017-03-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=":2" />。

危害消除於設計初期最為有效，成本較低且容易實現。而當工具已開始使用又或工序已經建立時則需要大幅度改變原來的工序<ref name=":1" />。若設計過程或生產階段中重新加入其他危害，則危害消除將會無效<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://machinerysafety101.com/2011/02/28/understanding-the-hierarchy-of-controls/|title=Understanding the Hierarchy of Controls|last=Nix|first=Doug|date=2011-02-28|website=Machinery Safety 101|access-date=2017-03-10|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224040755/https://machinerysafety101.com/2011/02/28/understanding-the-hierarchy-of-controls/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

將危害完全消除是[[设计保障安全|设计保障安全]]理念中的重要一環，該理念要求在項目的設計階段盡早消除危害<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/topics/ptd/|title=Prevention through Design|last=|first=|date=2016-07-29|website=U.S. National Institute for Occupational Safety and Health|language=en-us|access-date=2017-03-09|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206033512/https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/topics/ptd/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。將危害完全消除常為最困難的方式，但將項目設計初期將其提出有助設計者更容易作出安全相關的改變。

== 常見例子 ==
不再使用有害化學物質是危害消除的一個例子<ref name="NYCOSH" />，部分物質難以完全消除，則可以用其他較低危害的[[危害替代|替代]]<ref name=":0" />。危害消除亦可用於設備之上，例如將引起{{tsl|en|Health effects from noise|噪音引致的健康影響|噪音}}的設備從房間中移除<ref name="saunions">{{cite web|url=http://www.saunions.org.au/ohs/hierachy_of_controls.htm|title=Hierarchy of Controls|website={{tsl|en|SA Unions|}}|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050623055058/http://www.saunions.org.au/ohs/hierachy_of_controls.htm|archive-date=2005-06-23|accessdate=2017-03-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，又或將非必要的刀片從機械中移除<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=http://simplifiedsafety.com/blog/the-hierarchy-of-controls-part-one-elimination-and-substitution/|title=The Hierarchy of Controls, Part One: Elimination and Substitution|last=Braun|first=John|date=|website=Simplified Safety Fall Protection Blog|access-date=2017-03-10|archive-date=2017-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170926002702/http://simplifiedsafety.com/blog/the-hierarchy-of-controls-part-one-elimination-and-substitution/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。定期維修保養亦可消除故障做成的危害<ref name="saunions" />。

危害消除亦可應用於工序之上，例如不於高處行走可消除高空工作帶來的墮下危害<ref name="hse UK">{{cite web|url=http://www.hse.gov.uk/treework/safety-topics/height.htm#control|title=Tree Work – Working at height|last=|first=|date=|website=UK {{tsl|en|Health and Safety Executive|}}|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-14|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202092614/https://www.hse.gov.uk/treework/safety-topics/height.htm#control|dead-url=no}}</ref>，又或將需作維修保養的物件帶至地表才開始工作<ref name="NYCOSH" />。於[[穀倉塔|穀倉塔]]或其他高風險環境工作的工序可利用機械人或其他設備，由此消除人員在內所帶來的危害<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://progressivesafety.us/uncategorized/hierarchy-of-controls-prioritizes-action-on-workplace-hazards/|title=Hierarchy of Controls Prioritizes Action on Workplace Hazards|last=Mlynek|first=Joe|date=|work=Progressive Safety Services|access-date=2017-03-10|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125200919/http://progressivesafety.us/uncategorized/hierarchy-of-controls-prioritizes-action-on-workplace-hazards/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。減省打開包裹的工序亦可消除檢查員吸入有害物質的危害<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/docs/2014-102/default.html|title=Current Strategies for Engineering Controls in Nanomaterial Production and Downstream Handling Processes|last=|first=|date=November 2013|website=U.S. National Institute for Occupational Safety and Haalth|pages=9–10|language=en-us|access-date=2017-03-05|archive-date=2019-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190810151819/https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/docs/2014-102/default.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

